defaultThe Local Government Association (LGA) is the national voice of local government. We work with councils to support, promote and improve local government. 
default&#xa0;
default1.2
default 
defaultWe are a 
defaultpolitically-led, cross party organisation which works on behalf of councils to ensure local government has a strong, credible voice with national government. We aim to influence and set the political agenda on issues that matter to councils so that they ar
defaulte able to deliver local solutions to national problems.
