default1.3
default 
defaultUniversal Credit presents an opportunity to provide a more seamless support offer to claimants that will enable them to become more motivated, resilient and self-reliant.  For this to be realised cou
defaultncils must have a lead role in commissioning local support services, and local partnerships must be at the heart of delivery.
