default6.1
default 
defaultThe most desirable and sustainable way to support those affected by the reforms is, of course, to help them 
defaultinto work.
default 
defaultCouncils are
default 
defaultdriving local growth, and 
defaultprovide and/or commission services to
default help residents with more complex barriers to employment benefit from it.
default&#xa0;
default6.2
default 
defaultFar too many councils
default’
default are still reporting that J
defaultob 
defaultC
defaultentre 
defaultP
defaultlus (JCP)
default colleagues are unable to share information on clients and are 
defaultprevented from engaging
